cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with computer vision approaches for classification on a new dataset of crystallography diffraction patterns. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of AutoML optimization tools, which suggests that cs.DL (Deep Learning) could also be a relevant category. Finally, the paper deals with image classification, which could also make cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category.
